info.additionalInfo:
如想保留播放页的好友听歌弹出菜单只显示好友不显示热门主播.替换成

/* 屏蔽热门直播间 */
.popup-content {display: none !important; z-index: 1 !important;} 
.user-list-panel .seiya-tab-view .tabs .tab[data-name="talent"]{display: none !important;} 
.user-list-panel .seiya-tab-view .tabs .tab[data-name="friend"]{width: 100% !important;} 
.talent-list-wrap{display: none !important;}
.user-list-panel .items .item:first-of-type{display: none !important;}
.user-list-panel .items .item:nth-of-type(2){display: block !important;}
/*#player-main {z-index: 3000 !important;}*/

